* {{cite web|last1=Ackerman|first1=Spencer|last2=Roberts|first2=Dan|title=NSA phone surveillance program likely unconstitutional, federal judge rules|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/dec/16/nsa-phone-surveillance-likely-unconstitutional-judge|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2 January 2017|date=16 December 2013}}
